;B[pr]LB[rs:1][qr:2][qs:3][pr:4]C[Dia.1 The 2,1 point

The 2,1 point in this case doesn't help us as it doesn't kill off Black.  Black will connect at 2 and then at 4, so that he lives in Bik (mutual life).  The 2,1 point can't always come to the rescue.
