;W[rs]LB[qr:1][pr:2][rs:3][qs:A]C[Dia.2 Pae is a failure

White 1 is a good start and of course Black will dansu at 2.  The problem is White 3 starts a Pae, and that's not what we're going for here.  White can unconditionally capture Black.
