;W[rs]LB[qs:1][os:2][rs:3][ss:A]C[Dia.3 Correct / Connect

Instead of starting a Pae White should connect at 1.  Black doesn't have enough liberties to make an eye on the inside so he has to played 2.  White will play 3, and this is a dead shape for Black.  If he captures at A White will just kill him.
